==Documentation==
This template creates a full location page layout with hero section, tabs, wiki content, and sidebar.
Uses Semantic MediaWiki for structured data storage and display.

Locations are places that appear in video games, such as cities, planets, dungeons, or fictional worlds.

===Parameters===
{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Parameter !! Description
|-
|| Name || Display name of the location
|-
|| Guid || Giant Bomb API identifier
|-
|| Aliases || Alternative names (comma-separated)
|-
|| Image || Location image filename
|-
|| Deck || Short description shown in hero
|-
|| Games || Games featuring this location (comma-separated)
|-
|| Characters || Characters associated with this location (comma-separated)
|-
|| Concepts || Concepts related to this location (comma-separated)
|-
|| Locations || Related/similar locations (comma-separated)
|-
|| Objects || Objects found in this location (comma-separated)
|}

===Usage===
<pre>
